T02D3526:168b-1: badzra dh'a tv'i shva r'i m'a r'i tsyee s'a dha nam /
T02D3526:168b-3: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma 'od zer can gyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3526:169a-1: ma 'od zer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3526:169a-2: aom a'a:h'um sv'a h'a zhes pas spyi bo dang dpral ba dang /
T02D3526:169a-4: snying ga dang pus mo gnyis rnams su bdag nyid
T02D3526:169a-5: rnam par bsgoms nas aom yig gis thams cad sngon
T02D3526:169a-6: ma bzhin du rnam par dag par brjod pa'o //
T02D3526:169a-7: mthar thug pa'i chog byas nas aom yig las skyes
T02D3526:169a-8: pa'i ro rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma 'od zer
T02D3526:169a-10: zhal dmar po lto ba 'phyang ba /
T02D3526:169a-11: dbu skra kham pa gyen du 'bar zhing brdzis pa
T02D3526:169a-12: thod pa'i phreng ba can sprul gyi ske rags byas
T02D3526:169a-13: pa / stag gi pags pa'i na bza' mnabs pa /
T02D3526:169a-14: zhabs zung gis bgegs dpag tu med pa mnan pa /
T02D3526:169a-15: mchod rten gyi nang na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la zhabs g-yon brkyang gis bzhugs pa /
T02D3526:169a-16: rnam par snang mdzad kyis mgon dang bcas pa /
T02D3526:169a-17: sna tshogs pa'i phag gnyis kyis bkug pa'i yid kyis shing rta la zhon pa /
T02D3526:169a-22: dkar po rnams dang po la sogs pa'i zhal lnga'o //
T02D3526:169a-23: steng du phag zhal nag po gcig go / phyag
T02D3526:169a-24: g-yas pa rnams na ral gri dang gtun shing dang
T02D3526:169a-27: rdo rje rtse gcig pa dang /
T02D3526:169a-29: phyag g-yon pa rnams na zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub dang /
T02D3526:169a-31: mya ngan med pa'i yal ga dang /
T02D3526:169a-36: ljags bskyod cing zhal gtsigs pa /
T02D3526:169a-37: shin tu 'jigs par byed pa bsam par bya'o //
T02D3526:169a-38: shing rta'i dbus su phyag gnyis pa sdigs mdzub dang
T02D3526:169a-39: mya ngan na med pa'i yal ga phyag na bsnams
T02D3526:169a-40: pa'o // shing rta 'dren pa g-yon brkyang gis gnas pa 'jigs par byed pa bsam par bya'o //
T02D3526:169a-41: spro ba la sogs pa sngon du 'gro bas sems can gdug pa can rnams rengs pa dang /
T02D3526:169a-43: aom badzra dh'a tv'i shva r'i sarba dusht'a satv'an ha na ha na /
T02D3526:169a-45: pa tsa pa tsa aom m'a r'i tsyee aom h'um sv'a h'a zhes pa'i sngags bzlas par bya'o //
